https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/196. Document the JWT util and added a startup script for OA4MP installs to create a set of signing keys.
Update of website. Added support for echoing requests in CLC.

Updates to store API for QDL.
Renamed teh QDL modules' namespace to start with oa4mp, not the old oa2. Added Java serialization to someclasses to make sure QDL's contract of still (for now) allowing it is not broken.
Checkin before break, massive doc update
https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/211. Fixed with regression test. Tests for client credentials flow added.
https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/212. Added lots of tests for the new client credentials flow using RFC 7523 and lots of tweaks to tests.
Installer improvements, derby SQL isntall script was incomplete. Webiste/documentation improvements from 6.0 integrated.
https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/175 fix. Dedicated Tomcat instance for OA4MP know has .well-known pages as per RFC 8414.
Fix for https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/218. Changed package and some class names related to virtual issuers.
https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/219, https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/216 (more VO renaming of internal variables to vi)

Rebuild of website, fixed a few issues with PDFs, added index.html for https://jira.ncsa.illinois.edu/browse/CIL-2143 and https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/229
